"{\"uid\": \"rnz.co.nz-news-olympics-2024-524573-olympics-2024-dame-lisa-carrington-claims-sixth-gold-medal-with-win-in-women-s-kayak-fours\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The queen of kayaking has added another crown to her collection.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 64, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The country's most successful Olympian, Dame Lisa Carrington, has won a seventh medal and sixth gold, after spearheading the women's kayak four in their 500-metre final in Paris.\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.998800670245932, \"rank\": 0.001200769864069927, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Carrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lisa Carrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Carrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Carrington\"}, {\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999951694463, \"rank\": 4.83045998221896e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the first Olympic medal for the other three members of the crew, Alicia Hoskin, Olivia Brett and Tara Vaughan.\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The win takes New Zealand's medal tally to 12.\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8542523610109731, \"rank\": 0.12785875218536347, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The New Zealand crew celebrates after their win.Photo:AFP/OLIVIER MORIN  New Zealand powered out to first position at the start, but the German crew sneaked up on them approaching the 250m mark.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8542523610109731, \"rank\": 0.12785875218536347, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 486, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8542523610109731, \"rank\": 0.12785875218536347, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.96617642081691, \"rank\": 0.03155378715300486, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany then edged out in front to set up a thrilling finish.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8512939205769352, \"rank\": 0.13633493155880294, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carrington's crew proved too quick however, getting to the line in one minute and 32 seconds.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrington_family\", \"score\": 0.9999999618773935, \"rank\": 3.812231368545784e-08, \"text\": \"Carrington\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrington_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrington_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After getting out of the water, the women hugged each other tightly in celebration.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The crew share a hug.Photo:AFP/OLIVIER MORIN  Speaking to Sky Sport, Brett said she was \\\"so proud\\\" of her boatmates.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.999999987344154, \"rank\": 1.2655746404676237e-08, \"text\": \"Sky Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was an epic race and I am just so excited.\\\"\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaughan said she was \\\"so grateful\\\" to the other three women.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Vaughan\", \"score\": 0.9999697899042936, \"rank\": 3.020862425806071e-05, \"text\": \"Vaughan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Vaughan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Vaughan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being a part of this team is absolutely the best.\\\"\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hoskin said the plan was to \\\"stay in our own boat\\\" and trust the strategy that had been put in place.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So proud, like it takes a lot of courage to do that.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are really happy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carrington said the team, and everyone behind them, had put a lot of work into the Olympic campaign.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrington_family\", \"score\": 0.9999999618773935, \"rank\": 3.812231368545784e-08, \"text\": \"Carrington\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrington_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrington_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is an incredibly special moment, especially to just be able to do it on our biggest stage, so yeah, it's surreal.\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You just do not know when you line up.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You never know what the results are going to be be.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's amazing when you can come through, as we have.\\\"\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a92024,Radio New Zealand  NZ cyclist Ellesse Andrews has won the women's keirin final comfortably, while Lisa Carrington's crew have claimed a win in the K4.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.9891290856280915, \"rank\": 0.010990389960174164, \"text\": \"Radio New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}, {\"begin\": 1737, \"end\