her\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aimee Fisher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Fisher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Fisher\"}, {\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Carrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lisa Carrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Carrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Carrington\"}, {\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Fisher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aimee Fisher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Fisher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aimee_Fisher\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Alexandra kayaker won in a thrilling race and says he can not comprehend beating the world champion.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2156, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 0.999991242146431, \"rank\": 8.752029896525351e-06, \"text\": \"Alexandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandra_of_Denmark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"for ad-free news and current affairs  Olympics 2024 RSS  Follow RNZ News\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 0.9995319216765198, \"rank\": 0.0004681955372717367, \"text\": \"RSS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}, {\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RN